## Performance Optimizations

### CSS
- CSS Variables for theme switching (no DOM manipulation)
- Hardware-accelerated animations (transform, opacity)
- Minimal repaints (use will-change sparingly)
- Optimized selectors

### JavaScript
- Event delegation where possible
- Efficient DOM queries (caching elements)
- localStorage instead of memory for persistence
- Async/await for API calls
- Debouncing for input (auto-resize)

### Network
- Single API request per message (no polling)
- Efficient payload sizes
- Gzip compression (server-side)
- No unnecessary dependencies

### Rendering
- Lazy rendering of chat history
- Virtual scrolling not needed (small datasets)
- CSS animations (GPU accelerated)
- Minimal DOM operations

